column2: SELECT   d.sdss_s_ra AS input_ra, d.sdss_s_dec AS input_dec, s.ra as s_ra, s.dec as s_dec, s.z as s_z, s.specObjID, p.objID,   p.petroRad_u, p.petroRad_g, p.petroRad_r, p.petroRad_i, p.petroRad_z,   p.petroRadErr_u, p.petroRadErr_g, p.petroRadErr_r, p.petroRadErr_i, p.petroRadErr_z into mydb.MyTable from MyDB.CAGN_final_radec AS d     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( d.sdss_s_ra, d.sdss_s_dec, #) AS n      LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON n.objid=s.bestObjID      LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON n.objid=p.objID
